<%- include("includes/header.ejs") -%>

<%- include("includes/navbar.ejs") -%>

<main>
   <!-- Hero Section -->
   <section class="hero text-white text-center py-5 position-relative"
      style="background-image: url('/assets/image1.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center; height: 60vh;">
      <div class="container h-100">
         <div class="row h-100 align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-6 mx-auto">
               <div class="p-4 rounded-lg shadow-lg position-relative" style="backdrop-filter: blur(6px);">
                  <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold text-light">Welcome to Our Website</h1>
                  <p class="lead text-light">Discover a world of amazing books.</p>
                  <a href="/books" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Explore</a>
               </div>
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>
   </section>

   <!-- Benefits of Reading Section -->
   <section class="py-5 container">
      <div class="text-center py-4">
         <h2 class="fw-bold">Why Reading Books?</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="accordion" id="accordionExample">
         <!-- Benefit 1: Improved Mental Health -->
         <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header">
               <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne"
                  aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                  Improved Mental Health
               </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
               <div class="accordion-body">
                  Reading has been linked to reduced stress, improved focus, and better overall mental well-being. It
                  allows
                  you to escape into different worlds and perspectives, providing relief from the demands of daily life.
               </div>
            </div>
         </div>

         <!-- Benefit 2: Expanded Knowledge -->
         <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header">
               <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                  data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                  Expanded Knowledge
               </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
               <div class="accordion-body">
                  Reading exposes you to a wide range of information, ideas, and perspectives. It's a powerful tool for
                  expanding your knowledge, learning about different cultures, and staying informed about the world
                  around
                  you.
               </div>
            </div>
         </div>

         <!-- Benefit 3: Relaxation and Stress Reduction -->
         <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header">
               <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                  data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                  Relaxation and Stress Reduction
               </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
               <div class="accordion-body">
                  Reading can be a wonderful way to unwind and reduce stress. It provides a calming escape, helping you
                  find
                  relaxation and inner peace in the midst of a busy and often stressful world.
               </div>
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>
   </section>

</main>

<%- include("includes/footer.ejs") -%>